# CLAUDE.md

## Setup

```bash
task setup   # install dependencies and set up pre-commit hooks
```

## Common Commands

```bash
task check       # run lint, format, and typecheck (use before committing)
task test        # run tests
task lint        # run linter (ruff check --fix)
task format      # format code (ruff format)
task typecheck   # run type checker (pyright)
```

`task check` runs lint → format → typecheck in sequence. Run this before pushing.

## Running Individual Tools

```bash
uv run ruff check       # lint only
uv run ruff format      # format only
uv run pyright          # type check only
uv run pytest           # test only
```

